data.description: This well cared for home is move in ready, and has had some recent updates including all energy efficient windows throughout. The kitchen has been updated and is fully applianced and has tiled flooring. You'll be impressed with the beautiful solid hardwood flooring throughout. This has a neutral paint pallet throughout to easily blend with any decor. Trees in the back were removed and would make for a great patio area. The side yard is quite spacious to the north. This is a very easy distance to the U of I campus and the downtown area and close to Blair Park and the tennis courts.
